            "worstRating": "1"
          },
          "reviewBody": "Schools not only teach us to be good students but also to be good people. There were quite a few opportunities for me to take part in multiple debate competitions where I was given the chance to represent my school. Every time I see my school bus it brings back memories and I wish that I could just jump onto the bus and go back to school. Even while collecting my leaving certificate I was lost in all the good memories that I had there, pondering if I would get such good friends and teachers again. When I pass on a road close to my school, I feel like taking a detour to visit my school, so that I could visit my teachers, to reminisce about all the good times that I had here.",
          "publisher": {
            "@type": "Organization",
            "name": "Yellow Slate"
          }
        },
