            "ratingValue": "5",
            "bestRating": "5",
            "worstRating": "1"
          },
          "reviewBody": "PIS Pimpri is one of the best school with ICSE. As a teacher of Podar Prep, I can say under the guidance of Principal ma'am  the methods of teaching are outstanding, due to which the students have benefited alot.\nOut come of this is the results of 10th and 12th which are outstanding every year.\nI would like to say it's a proud moment for principal ma'am and all teachers.",
