        {
          "@type": "Review",
          "itemReviewed": {
            "@type": "School",
            "name": "Podar International School - Pune (Pimpri) - Chikhali"
          },
          "author": {
            "@type": "Person",
            "name": "Pro Queen"
          },
          "datePublished": "2024-06-05",
          "reviewRating": {
            "@type": "Rating",
            "ratingValue": "5",
            "bestRating": "5",
            "worstRating": "1"
          },
          "reviewBody": "PIS, Pimpri is the most important turning point of my life. Heartfelt gratitude to my respected and dearest Principal, You are a rock star🎸⭐️. It's all because of you honourable Ma'am that I have reached at this aspect of my life. Kudos and credits to you, for your support and guidance. Would have been lost if it was not you Ma'am. So many failing results but you and my dear teachers didn't give up upon me which striked my inner being and arose the extrovert me. The countless efforts, the sleepless nights and the encouraging words always beat within me like my heartbeat.\nIt's been four years and still can't overcome being a part of my favorite dwelling, my PIS, Pimpri. Thanks to one and all member there, who took so much efforts to help me climb the ladder which felt like it was kept on the wavering land.\nAn honest recommendation from me to the viewers, don't think a second and head towards enrollment. I'm sure one day you'll put in your story here and another would be a testimonial.\nStrong headed teachers, with firm foundation of concept clearance, integrity in PTA, plentiful events with well grooming of students for active participation on all activities, nurturing 21st century skills, healthy atmosphere, well maintained classrooms with AV learning tools, helping maids, knowledgeable admins and patience level is always maintained pertaining the crowd.\nIf I don't add a full stop here it will be an essay more than a review. 😬\nLast but not the least,\nYou ENROLL➡️ You ENRICH➡️ You ENCOUNTER ➡️ You are the EVIDENCE",
          "publisher": {
            "@type": "Organization",
            "name": "Yellow Slate"
          }
        }
